{"tid":1742160,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［民陣吹雞］12.8 民陣國際人權日集會","createTime":"2019-11-20T16:00:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T16:55:53.000Z","uid":49018,"like":63,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"52234df9d55dbbabaef775d50fd4836d6317d8f0","tid":1742160,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:00:29.000Z","msg":"【守護香港．和你同行】<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;12.8 民陣國際人權日集會<br />\n<br />\n自 1950 年起，聯合國把每年的 12 月 10 日定為「國際人權日」。世界人權逐步完善，向前發展；但香港的人權狀況卻不斷倒退。<br />\n<br />\n今年六月至今，香港人奮不顧身抵擋破壞人權的惡法，付上沉重代價：不少人權捍衛者受到警察暴力而嚴重受傷、近五千名示威者被捕，當中更包括未成年者和人道救援人員。政制繼續不義，行政機關濫權、任由警察執法不公；北京更開始抨擊香港司法裁決，威脅要剝奪違憲審查權。香港人權和人道危機，經已到達臨界點。<br />\n<br />\n根據《基本法》第 39 條和現行法例，適用於香港的聯合國人權公約共有十五條，其中七條訂明要求締約國包括香港提交報告。故此，香港本來是捍衛國際人權的一員。如今香港人權保障被政權不斷破壞，社會各界豈能繼續沉默，任由捍衛人權的前線人員受害？<br />\n<br />\n今年國際人權日步入 70 周年，民陣決定在 12 月 8 日（星期日）日間舉辦大型集會，呼籲全港市民出席，要求香港政府恪守《世界人權宣言》和適用於香港的聯合國人權公約，履行國際人權責任，維護人道主義和人性尊嚴。<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線<br />\n2019 年 11 月 20 日<br />\n<br />\n【集會時間地點】<br />\n12.8 星期日 Sunday<br />\n2-6PM<br />\n維多利亞公園 Victoria Park<br />\n不反對通知書申請中<br />\n<br />\n#守護香港  #和你同行<br />\n#StandUp4HumanRights<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P2KL69n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP2KL69n.jpg&h=aa2d8988&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec73d2da9b7c534b0fe3d13e66f9a3c03027ede","tid":1742160,"uid":42662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e82f83fc84ade6c29c89e8abcdeea3e25589f5","tid":1742160,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:01:02.000Z","msg":"幫我推上去！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fceecf7c7e8b77c546c39059a6fa4d0a873f002d","tid":1742160,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:01:21.000Z","msg":"美麗島事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2614af5a234e2091874a42e96c4a7afc333c7a38","tid":1742160,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:01:25.000Z","msg":"推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"801fd98c93917885dee57965e6b23d97fb0c9323","tid":1742160,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:01:55.000Z","msg":"和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c7ee5070d28c8d5fe396caf6a787b5fbbfb828","tid":1742160,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:02:35.000Z","msg":"大力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />吹大雞"},{"pid":"818975491d031fde10de2cf94f406f980676acdf","tid":1742160,"uid":274723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63983a47a832fb3c742d2f1512be1963094c3861","tid":1742160,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"818975491d031fde10de2cf94f406f980676acdf","tid":1742160,"uid":274723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr